==Gameplay Notes==
===Special Mechanics===
* Able to perform OASW at 60ASW.
* Provides luck, ASW or HP when used for modernization. Please see [[Modernization]] for more details.

===Overview===
* Low firepower, HP and armour.
* Good ASW.

